83rd OREGON LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY--2026 Regular Session
SENATE AMENDMENTS TO
A-ENGROSSED HOUSE BILL 4128
By COMMITTEE ON HOUSING AND DEVELOPMENT
February 25
